  <view aria-role="alert" class="hint_content">
    <view class="hint_title">温馨提示</view>
    <view class="hint_txt">
      <view>您的手机（{{phoneModel}}）暂不支持数字人导航功能，且导航体验可能有限，正在全力研发优化中，敬请期待~</view>
    </view>
    <view aria-role="button" aria-label="确定"  class="hint_btn" bindtap="closeVKno">
      确 定
      <!-- <view class="end_info_btn" bindtap="closeEndInfo">确 定</view> -->
    </view>
    <view class="hint_operate">
      <view></view>
